file.name: output.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
paths:
  /user:
    get:
      tags:
        - user
      summary: Get user
      description: This can only be done by the logged in user.
      operationId: getUser
      responses:
        default:
          description: successful operation
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Token.Id'
components:
  schemas:
    Token.Id:
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          example: 10
